\end_layout

\end_inset

: 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
P\left(G_{1}|E\right)=\frac{P\left(G_{1}\cap E\right)}{P\left(E\right)}=\frac{P\left(E|G_{1}\right)P\left(G_{1}\right)}{P\left(E\right)}.
\]

